    "excerpt": "While we focus on the Temple's destruction and all that is related to the ninth of Av I believe that our internal work reflects how we see and perceive the external.  . . .",
    "content": "\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"/translate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Contribute a translation</a></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Source (English)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nwithin the broken walls of the temple lives<br />\nthe history of the destructions<br />\nhonor, remember, mourn\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nwe will most likely not<br />\nbuild that third temple for the<br />\nre-building now is from within\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\ndeconstruct your temples,<br />\nthe ones that donâ€™t work<br />\nhonor, remember, mourn\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nreconstructing the self<br />\nbuild the internal tabernacle<br />\nthat cannot be taken away\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nhelp others to build their own<br />\ntemples, there own relationship<br />\nwith the Infinite\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nlisten to your Torah<br />\nresurrection and<br />\nnew beginnings will come\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n",
